    "dbq_title": "inyandiko-Based ikibazo",
    "dbq_text": "inyandiko-Based ikibazo: umunyeshure sesengura primary sources, build evidence-based arguments, and kora imyitozo the central ubuhinga of social-studies + ELA igenzura. Generates imvo inyandiko, scaffolded ikibazo, and inyishu keys aligned to your urwego.",
    "quiz_mode_title": "Pick the right ikizamini uburyo",
    "quiz_mode_text": "Hitamwo what iki ikizamini is for. Exit Ticket checks today’s learning. Pre-Check probes prior knowledge before teaching and surfaces gaps as concept ikarata with a one-kanda \"Explain to ishuri\" AI broadcast. Formative Check is a vyihuta mid-isomo pulse. Spaced Review tracks each umunyeshure’s cross-igihe retention with a per-concept sparkline. Each uburyo tunes prompts, ikintu-type mix, and the live dashboard layout."
